<img id="photo27" onclick="expGallery72.growPicture('7','2');expGallery72.trackGalleryImg('Report: Some 20 baseball players may face suspension in doping scandal')" class="cnnArticleBoxImage" width="640" height="360" border="0" src="http://i2.cdn.turner.com/cnn/dam/assets/120613105551-lance-armstrong-racing-horizontal-gallery.jpg" alt="Sport\'s era of shame?"/>
<cite id="cite27" class="expCaption"><span>Sport's era of shame?</span></cite>
</div>
</div>
